# Rule 4 shadows Rule 5 below it
# Rule 4 shadows Rule 6 below it
# Rule 8 shadows Rule 9 below it
# Rule 8 shadows Rule 10 below it
# Rule 8 shadows Rule 11 below it
# Rule 8 shadows Rule 12 below it
# Rule 8 shadows Rule 13 below it
# Rule 8 shadows Rule 14 below it
# Rule 8 shadows Rule 20 below it
# Rule 8 shadows Rule 21 below it
# Rule 8 shadows Rule 27 below it
# Rule 8 shadows Rule 28 below it
# Rule 0 shadows Rule 3 below it
# Rule 4 shadows Rule 5 below it
# Rule 4 shadows Rule 6 below it
# Rule 8 shadows Rule 9 below it
# Rule 8 shadows Rule 10 below it
# Rule 8 shadows Rule 11 below it
# Rule 8 shadows Rule 12 below it
# Rule 8 shadows Rule 13 below it
# Rule 8 shadows Rule 14 below it
# Rule 8 shadows Rule 20 below it
# Rule 8 shadows Rule 21 below it
# Rule 8 shadows Rule 27 below it
